inv_logit <- function(logit) exp(logit) / (1 + exp(logit))

logodds2_trt2 <- b02 + as.matrix(trt_cov) %*% as.matrix(bi_trt2) + trt_eff2

prob_2to3_trt1 <- inv_logit(logodds1_trt1)

for (i in 1:nrow(df_trt_true)){
  for(j in 1:nrow(df_ctrl_true)){

      if (df_trt_true[i,1] > df_ctrl_true[j,1]){
        trtwin_true[i,j] = 1
        ctrlwin_true[i,j] = 0
      }
      else if (df_trt_true[i,1] < df_ctrl_true[j,1]){
        trtwin_true[i,j] = 0
        ctrlwin_true[i,j] = 1

        trtwin_true[i,j] = 1
        ctrlwin_true[i,j] = 0

df_trt_comp <- data.frame(outcomes_trt1, outcomes_trt2)

##############IPS-Weighted########################################




colnames(df_trt_comp) <- c("outcomes_comb1", "outcomes_comb2")
colnames(df_ctrl_comp) <- c("outcomes_comb1", "outcomes_comb2")

df_comb <- rbind(df_trt_comp, df_ctrl_comp)
df_comb$treatment <- c(rep(1,n_count), rep(0,n_count))
df_comb$x1 <- c(x1_trt, x1_ctrl)
df_comb$x2 <- c(x2_trt, x2_ctrl)
df_comb$x3 <- c(x3_trt, x3_ctrl)
df_comb$x4 <- c(x4_trt, x4_ctrl)
df_comb$x5 <- c(x5_trt, x5_ctrl)
df_comb$x6 <- c(x6_trt, x6_ctrl)

###PS
PropScore <- glm(treatment~x1 + x2 + x3 + x4 + x5 + x6, 
                 data = df_comb, family=binomial)
pi_func <- fitted(PropScore)

g_hfunc_IPS1 <- matrix(0, nrow = 2*nrow(df_trt_comp), ncol = 2*nrow(df_ctrl_comp))
g_hfunc_IPS2 <- matrix(0, nrow = 2*nrow(df_trt_comp), ncol = 2*nrow(df_ctrl_comp))

for (i in 1:(2*n_count-1)){
  for(j in (i+1):(2*n_count)){

      if (df_comb[i,1] > df_comb[j,1]){
        g_hfunc_IPS1[i,j] = (0.5)*(df_comb[i,"treatment"]*(1-df_comb[j,"treatment"])*1/(pi_func[i]*(1-pi_func[j])))
        g_hfunc_IPS2[i,j] = 0
      }
      else if (df_comb[i,1] < df_comb[j,1]){
        g_hfunc_IPS1[i,j] = 0
        g_hfunc_IPS2[i,j] = (0.5)*(df_comb[i,"treatment"]*(1-df_comb[j,"treatment"])*1/(pi_func[i]*(1-pi_func[j])))
      }
      else if (df_comb[i,2] > df_comb[j,2]){
        g_hfunc_IPS1[i,j] = (0.5)*(df_comb[i,"treatment"]*(1-df_comb[j,"treatment"])*1/(pi_func[i]*(1-pi_func[j])))
        g_hfunc_IPS2[i,j] = 0
      }
      else if (df_comb[i,2] < df_comb[j,2]){
        g_hfunc_IPS1[i,j] = 0
        g_hfunc_IPS2[i,j] = (0.5)*(df_comb[i,"treatment"]*(1-df_comb[j,"treatment"])*1/(pi_func[i]*(1-pi_func[j])))
      }

  }
}



tau1_IPS <- sum(as.vector(g_hfunc_IPS1), na.rm = T)/(choose(2*n_count,2))
tau2_IPS <- sum(as.vector(g_hfunc_IPS2), na.rm = T)/(choose(2*n_count,2))



WR_sim_comp_IPS[sim_count] <- tau1_IPS/tau2_IPS









######################Overlap Weighting##############################


g_hfunc_OW1 <- matrix(0, nrow = 2*nrow(df_trt_comp), ncol = 2*nrow(df_ctrl_comp))
g_hfunc_OW2 <- matrix(0, nrow = 2*nrow(df_trt_comp), ncol = 2*nrow(df_ctrl_comp))

for (i in 1:(2*n_count-1)){
  for(j in (i+1):(2*n_count)){

      if (df_comb[i,1] > df_comb[j,1]){
        g_hfunc_OW1[i,j] = (0.5)*(df_comb[i,"treatment"]*(1-df_comb[j,"treatment"])*1*(1-pi_func[i])*pi_func[j])
        g_hfunc_OW2[i,j] = 0
      }
      else if (df_comb[i,1] < df_comb[j,1]){
        g_hfunc_OW1[i,j] = 0
        g_hfunc_OW2[i,j] = (0.5)*(df_comb[i,"treatment"]*(1-df_comb[j,"treatment"])*1*(1-pi_func[i])*pi_func[j])
      }
      else if (df_comb[i,2] > df_comb[j,2]){
        g_hfunc_OW1[i,j] = (0.5)*(df_comb[i,"treatment"]*(1-df_comb[j,"treatment"])*1*(1-pi_func[i])*pi_func[j])
        g_hfunc_OW2[i,j] = 0
      }
      else if (df_comb[i,2] < df_comb[j,2]){
        g_hfunc_OW1[i,j] = 0
        g_hfunc_OW2[i,j] = (0.5)*(df_comb[i,"treatment"]*(1-df_comb[j,"treatment"])*1*(1-pi_func[i])*pi_func[j])
      }

  }
}


tau1_OW <- sum(as.vector(g_hfunc_OW1), na.rm = T)/(choose(2*n_count,2))
tau2_OW <- sum(as.vector(g_hfunc_OW2), na.rm = T)/(choose(2*n_count,2))



WR_sim_comp_OW[sim_count] <- tau1_OW/tau2_OW




###############Doubly Robust Estimator################################


###DR mu-function

if((!(1 %in% df_comb[df_comb$treatment==1,]$outcomes_comb1) &
     !(2 %in% df_comb[df_comb$treatment==1,]$outcomes_comb1)) |
     (!(1 %in% df_comb[df_comb$treatment==0,]$outcomes_comb1) &
     !(2 %in% df_comb[df_comb$treatment==0,]$outcomes_comb1)) |
     (!(1 %in% df_comb[df_comb$treatment==1,]$outcomes_comb2) &
     !(2 %in% df_comb[df_comb$treatment==1,]$outcomes_comb2)) |
     (!(1 %in% df_comb[df_comb$treatment==0,]$outcomes_comb2) &
     !(2 %in% df_comb[df_comb$treatment==0,]$outcomes_comb2))){
  break
}

else {
dr_trt1 <- vglm(factor(outcomes_comb1) ~ x1 + x2 + x3 + x4 + x5 + x6, 
                data = df_comb[df_comb$treatment==1,], 
                family = multinomial)
dr_trt2 <- vglm(factor(outcomes_comb2) ~ x1 + x2 + x3 + x4 + x5 + x6, 
                data = df_comb[df_comb$treatment==1,], 
                family = multinomial)
dr_ctrl1 <- vglm(factor(outcomes_comb1) ~ x1 + x2 + x3 + x4 + x5 + x6, 
                data = df_comb[df_comb$treatment==0,], 
                family = multinomial)
dr_ctrl2 <- vglm(factor(outcomes_comb2) ~ x1 + x2 + x3 + x4 + x5 + x6, 
                data = df_comb[df_comb$treatment==0,], 
                family = multinomial)

cond_prob_trt1 <- predictvglm(dr_trt1, newdata = df_comb,
                              type = "response")
cond_prob_trt2 <- predictvglm(dr_trt2, newdata = df_comb, 
                              type = "response")
cond_prob_ctrl1 <- predictvglm(dr_ctrl1, newdata = df_comb, 
                               type = "response")
cond_prob_ctrl2 <- predictvglm(dr_ctrl2, newdata = df_comb, 
                               type = "response")
}

prob1_0 <-data.frame(rep(0,n_count))
colnames(prob1_0) <- "1"
prob2_0 <-data.frame(rep(0,n_count))
colnames(prob2_0) <- "2"





if(!"1" %in% colnames(cond_prob_trt1)){
  cond_prob_trt1 <- cbind(prob1_0, cond_prob_trt1)
}

if(!"1" %in% colnames(cond_prob_ctrl1)){
  cond_prob_ctrl1 <- cbind(prob1_0, cond_prob_ctrl1)
}
if(!"2" %in% colnames(cond_prob_trt1)){
  col1 <- data.frame(cond_prob_trt1[,1])
  colnames(col1) <- "1"
  col3 <- data.frame(cond_prob_trt1[,2])
  colnames(col3) <- "3"
  cond_prob_trt1 <- cbind(col1, prob2_0, col3)
}

if(!"2" %in% colnames(cond_prob_ctrl1)){
  col1 <- data.frame(cond_prob_ctrl1[,1])
  colnames(col1) <- "1"
  col3 <- data.frame(cond_prob_ctrl1[,2])
  colnames(col3) <- "3"
  cond_prob_ctrl1 <- cbind(col1, prob2_0, col3)
}




if(!"1" %in% colnames(cond_prob_trt2)){
  cond_prob_trt2 <- cbind(prob1_0, cond_prob_trt2)
}

if(!"1" %in% colnames(cond_prob_ctrl2)){
  cond_prob_ctrl2 <- cbind(prob1_0, cond_prob_ctrl2)
}
if(!"2" %in% colnames(cond_prob_trt2)){
  col1 <- data.frame(cond_prob_trt2[,1])
  colnames(col1) <- "1"
  col3 <- data.frame(cond_prob_trt2[,2])
  colnames(col3) <- "3"
  cond_prob_trt2 <- cbind(col1, prob2_0, col3)
}

if(!"2" %in% colnames(cond_prob_ctrl2)){
  col1 <- data.frame(cond_prob_ctrl2[,1])
  colnames(col1) <- "1"
  col3 <- data.frame(cond_prob_ctrl2[,2])
  colnames(col3) <- "3"
  cond_prob_ctrl2 <- cbind(col1, prob2_0, col3)
}


#cond_prob1 <- rbind(cond_prob_trt1, cond_prob_ctrl1)
#cond_prob2 <- rbind(cond_prob_trt2, cond_prob_ctrl2)

g_hfunc_DR1 <- matrix(0, nrow = 2*nrow(df_trt_comp), ncol = 2*nrow(df_ctrl_comp))
g_hfunc_DR2 <- matrix(0, nrow = 2*nrow(df_trt_comp), ncol = 2*nrow(df_ctrl_comp))





for (i in 1:(2*n_count-1)){
  for(j in (i+1):(2*n_count)){

      if (df_comb[i,1] > df_comb[j,1]){
        g_hfunc_DR1[i,j] = (0.5)*((df_comb[i,"treatment"]*(1-df_comb[j,"treatment"])*1/(pi_func[i]*(1-pi_func[j])))-
                                  (df_comb[i,"treatment"]*(1-df_comb[j,"treatment"])/(pi_func[i]*(1-pi_func[j]))-1)*
                                           (cond_prob_trt1[i,2]*cond_prob_ctrl1[j,1]+
                                            cond_prob_trt1[i,3]*cond_prob_ctrl1[j,1]+

                                           (cond_prob_trt1[j,1]*cond_prob_ctrl1[i,2]+
                                            cond_prob_trt1[j,1]*cond_prob_ctrl1[i,3]+
                                            cond_prob_trt1[j,2]*cond_prob_ctrl1[i,3]+
                                            (
                                            cond_prob_trt1[j,1]*cond_prob_ctrl1[i,1]+
                                            cond_prob_trt1[j,2]*cond_prob_ctrl1[i,2]+
                                            cond_prob_trt1[j,3]*cond_prob_ctrl1[i,3]
                                            )*(
                                            cond_prob_trt2[j,1]*cond_prob_ctrl2[i,2]+
                                            cond_prob_trt2[j,1]*cond_prob_ctrl2[i,3]+
                                            cond_prob_trt2[j,2]*cond_prob_ctrl2[i,3]
                                            )
                                            )
                                            )
      }
      else if (df_comb[i,2] > df_comb[j,2]){
        
        g_hfunc_DROW1[i,j] = (0.5)*((df_comb[i,"treatment"]*(1-df_comb[j,"treatment"])*1*(1-pi_func[i])*pi_func[j])-
                                  (df_comb[i,"treatment"]*(1-df_comb[j,"treatment"])*(1-pi_func[i])*pi_func[j]-1)*
                                           (cond_prob_trt1[i,2]*cond_prob_ctrl1[j,1]+
                                            cond_prob_trt1[i,3]*cond_prob_ctrl1[j,1]+
                                            cond_prob_trt1[i,3]*cond_prob_ctrl1[j,2]+
                                            (
                                            cond_prob_trt1[i,1]*cond_prob_ctrl1[j,1]+
                                            cond_prob_trt1[i,2]*cond_prob_ctrl1[j,2]+
                                            cond_prob_trt1[i,3]*cond_prob_ctrl1[j,3]
                                            )*(
                                            cond_prob_trt2[i,2]*cond_prob_ctrl2[j,1]+
                                            cond_prob_trt2[i,3]*cond_prob_ctrl2[j,1]+
                                            cond_prob_trt2[i,3]*cond_prob_ctrl2[j,2]
                                            )
                                            ) + 0 -
                                    (df_comb[j,"treatment"]*(1-df_comb[i,"treatment"])*(1-pi_func[j])*pi_func[i]-1)*
                                           (cond_prob_trt1[j,2]*cond_prob_ctrl1[i,1]+
                                            cond_prob_trt1[j,3]*cond_prob_ctrl1[i,1]+
                                            cond_prob_trt1[j,3]*cond_prob_ctrl1[i,2]+
                                            (
                                            cond_prob_trt1[j,1]*cond_prob_ctrl1[i,1]+
                                            cond_prob_trt1[j,2]*cond_prob_ctrl1[i,2]+
                                            cond_prob_trt1[j,3]*cond_prob_ctrl1[i,3]
                                            )*(
                                            cond_prob_trt2[j,2]*cond_prob_ctrl2[i,1]+
                                            cond_prob_trt2[j,3]*cond_prob_ctrl2[i,1]+
                                            cond_prob_trt2[j,3]*cond_prob_ctrl2[i,2]
                                            ))
                                            )
        

        g_hfunc_DROW2[i,j] = (0.5)*(0 - 
                               (df_comb[i,"treatment"]*(1-df_comb[j,"treatment"])*(1-pi_func[i])*pi_func[j]-1)*
                                           (cond_prob_trt1[i,1]*cond_prob_ctrl1[j,2]+
                                            cond_prob_trt1[i,1]*cond_prob_ctrl1[j,3]+
                                            cond_prob_trt1[i,2]*cond_prob_ctrl1[j,3]+
                                            (
                                            cond_prob_trt1[i,1]*cond_prob_ctrl1[j,1]+
                                            cond_prob_trt1[i,2]*cond_prob_ctrl1[j,2]+
                                            cond_prob_trt1[i,3]*cond_prob_ctrl1[j,3]
                                            )*(
                                            cond_prob_trt2[i,1]*cond_prob_ctrl2[j,2]+
                                            cond_prob_trt2[i,1]*cond_prob_ctrl2[j,3]+
                                            cond_prob_trt2[i,2]*cond_prob_ctrl2[j,3]
                                            )
                                            ) +
                                 (df_comb[j,"treatment"]*(1-df_comb[i,"treatment"])*1*(1-pi_func[j])*pi_func[i])-
                                 (df_comb[j,"treatment"]*(1-df_comb[i,"treatment"])*(1-pi_func[j])*pi_func[i]-1)*
                                           (cond_prob_trt1[j,1]*cond_prob_ctrl1[i,2]+
                                            cond_prob_trt1[j,1]*cond_prob_ctrl1[i,3]+
                                            cond_prob_trt1[j,2]*cond_prob_ctrl1[i,3]+
                                            (
                                            cond_prob_trt1[j,1]*cond_prob_ctrl1[i,1]+
                                            cond_prob_trt1[j,2]*cond_prob_ctrl1[i,2]+
                                            cond_prob_trt1[j,3]*cond_prob_ctrl1[i,3]
                                            )*(
                                            cond_prob_trt2[j,1]*cond_prob_ctrl2[i,2]+
                                            cond_prob_trt2[j,1]*cond_prob_ctrl2[i,3]+
                                            cond_prob_trt2[j,2]*cond_prob_ctrl2[i,3]
                                            )
                                            )
                                            )
        
        
      }
    
      else if (df_comb[i,2] < df_comb[j,2]){
        g_hfunc_DROW1[i,j] = (0.5)*(0 -
                              (df_comb[i,"treatment"]*(1-df_comb[j,"treatment"])*(1-pi_func[i])*pi_func[j]-1)*
                                           (cond_prob_trt1[i,2]*cond_prob_ctrl1[j,1]+
                                            cond_prob_trt1[i,3]*cond_prob_ctrl1[j,1]+
                                            cond_prob_trt1[i,3]*cond_prob_ctrl1[j,2]+
                                            (
                                            cond_prob_trt1[i,1]*cond_prob_ctrl1[j,1]+
                                            cond_prob_trt1[i,2]*cond_prob_ctrl1[j,2]+
                                            cond_prob_trt1[i,3]*cond_prob_ctrl1[j,3]
                                            )*(
                                            cond_prob_trt2[i,2]*cond_prob_ctrl2[j,1]+
                                            cond_prob_trt2[i,3]*cond_prob_ctrl2[j,1]+
                                            cond_prob_trt2[i,3]*cond_prob_ctrl2[j,2]
                                            )
                                            ) +
                                (df_comb[j,"treatment"]*(1-df_comb[i,"treatment"])*1*(1-pi_func[j])*pi_func[i])-
                                (df_comb[j,"treatment"]*(1-df_comb[i,"treatment"])*(1-pi_func[j])*pi_func[i]-1)*
                                           (cond_prob_trt1[j,2]*cond_prob_ctrl1[i,1]+
                                            cond_prob_trt1[j,3]*cond_prob_ctrl1[i,1]+
                                            cond_prob_trt1[j,3]*cond_prob_ctrl1[i,2]+
                                            (
                                            cond_prob_trt1[j,1]*cond_prob_ctrl1[i,1]+
                                            cond_prob_trt1[j,2]*cond_prob_ctrl1[i,2]+
                                            cond_prob_trt1[j,3]*cond_prob_ctrl1[i,3]
                                            )*(
                                            cond_prob_trt2[j,2]*cond_prob_ctrl2[i,1]+
                                            cond_prob_trt2[j,3]*cond_prob_ctrl2[i,1]+
                                            cond_prob_trt2[j,3]*cond_prob_ctrl2[i,2]
                                            ))
                                            )
        
        g_hfunc_DROW2[i,j] = (0.5)*((df_comb[i,"treatment"]*(1-df_comb[j,"treatment"])*1*(1-pi_func[i])*pi_func[j])-
                                  (df_comb[i,"treatment"]*(1-df_comb[j,"treatment"])*(1-pi_func[i])*pi_func[j]-1)*
                                           (cond_prob_trt1[i,1]*cond_prob_ctrl1[j,2]+
                                            cond_prob_trt1[i,1]*cond_prob_ctrl1[j,3]+
                                            cond_prob_trt1[i,2]*cond_prob_ctrl1[j,3]+
                                            (
                                            cond_prob_trt1[i,1]*cond_prob_ctrl1[j,1]+
                                            cond_prob_trt1[i,2]*cond_prob_ctrl1[j,2]+
                                            cond_prob_trt1[i,3]*cond_prob_ctrl1[j,3]
                                            )*(
                                            cond_prob_trt2[i,1]*cond_prob_ctrl2[j,2]+
                                            cond_prob_trt2[i,1]*cond_prob_ctrl2[j,3]+
                                            cond_prob_trt2[i,2]*cond_prob_ctrl2[j,3]
                                            )
                                            )
                                            + 0 -
                                    (df_comb[j,"treatment"]*(1-df_comb[i,"treatment"])*(1-pi_func[j])*pi_func[i]-1)*
                                           (cond_prob_trt1[j,1]*cond_prob_ctrl1[i,2]+
                                            cond_prob_trt1[j,1]*cond_prob_ctrl1[i,3]+
                                            cond_prob_trt1[j,2]*cond_prob_ctrl1[i,3]+
                                            (
                                            cond_prob_trt1[j,1]*cond_prob_ctrl1[i,1]+
                                            cond_prob_trt1[j,2]*cond_prob_ctrl1[i,2]+
                                            cond_prob_trt1[j,3]*cond_prob_ctrl1[i,3]
                                            )*(
                                            cond_prob_trt2[j,1]*cond_prob_ctrl2[i,2]+
                                            cond_prob_trt2[j,1]*cond_prob_ctrl2[i,3]+
                                            cond_prob_trt2[j,2]*cond_prob_ctrl2[i,3]
                                            )
                                            )
                                            )
        
      }

  }
}

tau1_DROW <- sum(as.vector(g_hfunc_DROW1), na.rm = T) / (choose(2*n_count, 2))
